        <item>
          <title>A scrapyard worker injured in the UPS plane crash dies on Christmas, raising deaths to 15</title>
          <description><![CDATA[A Cuban immigrant who worked at a Kentucky scrapyard has died from severe burns suffered in last month’s UPS cargo plane crash, raising the death toll to 15 people.]]></description>
